1576056620--SELECT a.system_id,c.system_name,COUNT(1) AS counts, b.nums, SUM(deposit_money) AS total_deposit, SUM(express_money) AS total_express, SUM(take_price) AS take_money, SUM(other_money) AS other_money, SUM(prd_money) AS prd_express, a.ADDDATE, d.balance FROM u13123456789_drop_shipping_pay_log AS a 
				INNER JOIN (
					SELECT m.system_id,m.ADDDATE,m.balance FROM u13123456789_drop_shipping_pay_log AS m 
					INNER JOIN (
						SELECT MAX(id) AS id FROM u13123456789_drop_shipping_pay_log  where system_id = '13123456789'   GROUP BY ADDDATE
					) n ON m.id = n.id
				) d ON a.ADDDATE = d.ADDDATE
				LEFT JOIN (SELECT system_id,COUNT(1) AS nums,ADDDATE FROM u13123456789_drop_shipping_pay_log WHERE tid LIKE 'CZ%' GROUP BY system_id,ADDDATE) b
				ON a.system_id = b.system_id and a.ADDDATE = b.ADDDATE
				LEFT JOIN u13123456789_drop_shipping_client c ON a.system_id = c.system_id
				 where a.system_id = '13123456789' 
				GROUP BY a.system_id,a.adddate ORDER BY a.ADDTIME DESC limit 0,50
1576056620--SELECT a.system_id,c.system_name,COUNT(1) AS counts, b.nums, SUM(deposit_money) AS total_deposit, SUM(express_money) AS total_express, SUM(take_price) AS take_money, SUM(other_money) AS other_money, SUM(prd_money) AS prd_express, a.ADDDATE, d.balance FROM u13123456789_drop_shipping_pay_log AS a 
				INNER JOIN (
					SELECT m.system_id,m.ADDDATE,m.balance FROM u13123456789_drop_shipping_pay_log AS m 
					INNER JOIN (
						SELECT MAX(id) AS id FROM u13123456789_drop_shipping_pay_log  where system_id = '13123456789'   GROUP BY ADDDATE
					) n ON m.id = n.id
				) d ON a.ADDDATE = d.ADDDATE
				LEFT JOIN (SELECT system_id,COUNT(1) AS nums,ADDDATE FROM u13123456789_drop_shipping_pay_log WHERE tid LIKE 'CZ%' GROUP BY system_id,ADDDATE) b
				ON a.system_id = b.system_id and a.ADDDATE = b.ADDDATE
				LEFT JOIN u13123456789_drop_shipping_client c ON a.system_id = c.system_id
				 where a.system_id = '13123456789' 
				GROUP BY a.system_id,a.adddate ORDER BY a.ADDTIME DESC
